node.text:
Many people ask me "What is callalou?" Well besides being an excellent natural wig for your Poison Ivy costume, callalou or callaloo are the leaves of the amaranth root, and thus also known as amaranth! 
Similar to turnip greens in texture but with a slightly minty taste, these greens grow like gangbusters in many Caribbean islands often with salt pork and whole crab bodies for that good good flavor. I love making them into to patties cause it pairs so wonderfully with the turmeric dough

Still a few available for tomorrow's pickup, slide into my dm's and out that order in üåû
